title: Chloe Valdary 5: Her DJ Name is Paradox! And Why She Makes Friends with the Unknown
description:
Chloe's views on music, her work as a DJ, why she chose the DJ name "Paradox", and why the unknown is our best friend.

The whole conversation is here, including Chloe's life story and the history of the Theory of Enchantment, her views on Jordan Peterson, limitations, creativity and barbarians. https://youtu.be/ph8fi1iytwQ
